The media project worker.


Features:

- asynchronously search for torrents from multiple sites
- search for tv/anime next episodes/seasons
- fetch new releases from web sources (vcdquality releases, tvrage schedule, sputnikmusic reviews)
- search for new media which match releases filters (imdb rating, tvrage style, sputnikmusic rating)
- search for new media from the local media metadata (movies directors and actors, music similar bands)
- fetch subtitles for local video files
- unpack, clean and sort downloaded media into the media type based directories
- update local media metadata from web sources (imdb, tvrage, sputnikmusic)
- retrieve trailers and audio tracks for local media and new releases
- sync media to network hosts


Start the worker:
./mediaworker/run.py
